OL,3,CRAAC found in Borders hospital
OL,5,FNHS Borders is advising of disruption
OL,6,Fto services after discovering
OL,7,Fpotentially dangerous Reinforced
OL,8,FAutoclaved Aerated Concrete (RAAC) at
OL,9,Fone of its sites.
OL,11,FThe NHS board says the "safety of
OL,12,Fstaff and patients is paramount and
OL,13,Fthe decant of the Knoll hospital site,
OL,14,Fincluding Knoll Community Hospital,
OL,15,FHealth Centre, Duns Medical Group and
OL,16,FMerse Medical Practice will be
OL,17,Fundertaken as quickly as we safely
OL,18,Fcan".
