OL,3,CRAAC found in Borders hospital
OL,5,FNo clinics, appointments or inpatient
OL,6,Fcare will be provided from the
OL,7,Fpremises whilst the work is undertaken.
OL,9,FBosses are currently planning how to
OL,10,Fsafely move patients from the hospital/
OL,11,Fhealth centre and how services can be
OL,12,Fprovided elsewhere.
OL,14,FThere is currently no timeframe on
OL,15,Fwhen the work will take place.
OL,17,FIn 2023 it was widely reported that
OL,18,Fthe presence of RAAC was likely in
OL,19,Fproperties across the NHS Scotland
OL,20,Festate.
