OL,3,CRAAC found in Borders hospital
OL,5,FNHS Scotland completed a survey
OL,6,Fprogramme on behalf of the Scottish
OL,7,FGovernment to identify where RAAC
OL,8,Fexists in its estate.
OL,10,FThe initial surveys of NHS Borders
OL,11,Fbuildings where there was a potential
OL,12,Fpresence of RAAC were carried out on
OL,13,F14 and 15 September 2023.
OL,15,FThe surveys showed that RAAC was
OL,16,Fpresent in four NHS Borders buildings
OL,17,F(Knoll Hospital, Knoll Health Centre,
OL,18,FJedburgh Health Centre and Kelso
OL,19,FHospital).
