OL,3,CRAAC found in Borders hospital
OL,5,FAlthough RAAC was found to be present
OL,6,Fin these four locations, the expert
OL,7,Fsurveyors advised that there was no
OL,8,Fevidence at that stage of concrete
OL,9,Fbeing in poor condition resulting in
OL,10,Fan immediate risk, and therefore no
OL,11,Fcritical or immediate actions were
OL,12,Frequired at any of the sites.
OL,14,FThe initial surveys were undertaken
OL,15,Fbased on visual inspection with second
OL,16,Fphase surveys to be undertaken as
OL,17,Ffollow up.
