OL,3,CRAAC found in Borders hospital
OL,5,FDuring 2024, and in advance of the
OL,6,Fnational programme of second phase
OL,7,Fsurveys, NHS Borders commissioned in-
OL,8,Fdepth surveys to be carried out in the
OL,9,Fsites where the presence of RAAC had
OL,10,Fbeen identified.
OL,12,FOn Monday (27 January 2025), NHS
OL,13,FBorders was advised by the structural
OL,14,Fengineers who had undertaken the in-
OL,15,Fdepth surveys that there is an issue
OL,16,Fwith the roof construction at the
OL,17,FKnoll requiring action "as soon as
OL,18,Fpossible (within the next four weeks)".
