OL,3,CRAAC found in Borders hospital
OL,5,FA similar survey of Kelso Hospital is
OL,6,Fnow being finalised and there are
OL,7,Fcurrently no indications of issues at
OL,8,Fthat site.
OL,10,FThe phase two survey of Jedburgh
OL,11,FHealth Centre has not yet commenced.
OL,13,FChief Officer Chris Myers said: "We
OL,14,Frecognise that this information will
OL,15,Fcome as a shock to staff, patients and
OL,16,Feveryone who uses the services
OL,17,Fprovided from the Knoll Hospital and
OL,18,FHealth Centre, including patients from
OL,19,Fboth GP practices.
