OL,5,F"We are working at pace to identify
OL,6,Falternative locations from which
OL,7,Fservices will be provided whilst the
OL,8,Fremedial works are undertaken. As soon
OL,9,Fas we are in a position to confirm
OL,10,Fthese details they will be
OL,11,Fcommunicated directly to people
OL,12,Faffected and made available in the
OL,13,Fpublic domain on NHS Borders website.
