OL,5,F"There is inevitably going to be a
OL,6,Fperiod of disruption which we will of
OL,7,Fcourse work to minimise as far as
OL,8,Fpossible. I ask for patience whilst we
OL,9,Fwork through the details, and to
OL,10,Fenable our staff and partners to focus
OL,11,Fon the tasks at hand I respectfully
OL,12,Fask that people are not drawn into
OL,13,Funfounded speculation.
