OL,5,F"This is a temporary closure to the
OL,6,FKnoll and we are committed to
OL,7,Fundertaking these works. We are clear
OL,8,Fat this point that the relevant work
OL,9,Fwill be commissioned with a view to
OL,10,Freturning the Knoll Community Hospital
OL,11,Fand Health Centre to a fully
OL,12,Ffunctioning facility.
OL,14,F"Although tempting, please do not
OL,15,Fcontact the Knoll Hospital or GP
OL,16,Fpractice staff to ask about interim
OL,17,Farrangements. If you are directly
OL,18,Faffected with forthcoming appointments
OL,19,Fetc you will be contacted directly in
OL,20,Fdue course.
